                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="col-xl-6  col-12 order-1  d-lg-inline d-block text-center tutorial-text-wrapper">
                    <p class="tutorial-text">The food management system user interface comes in 6 different colors for
                        you to explore and choose your favorite.
                    </p>

