                                        <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="8" />
                                    </svg>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center my-4">
                <div class="col-12 d-xl-inline d-block tutorial-text-wrapper text-center">
                    <p class="tutorial-text">Keep in mind that this software still has a long way to go, with many more
                        features to be added in the future.
                        <br>
                        We are still in version 1.0.0 after all.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
